title: European Soc of Human Genetics
description:
This mobile app has been developed for the members of the European Society of Human Genetics and the participants of the yearly ESHG Conferences, which are one of the premier events in Human Genetics worldwide.
Access all relevant society topics and the entire conference information such as sessions, presentations, posters, abstracts, exhibitors & maps. Browse sessions by day, topic, types & tracks. Create your personalised congress programme (synchronised with your online Scientific Programme & Planner). Vote & Ask questions during the “Mobile app interactive sessions”. In addition, find all the practical information about conference. 
Before the first use, you will need to download the latest society and conference data. Afterwards, you will have offline access to the app. Note that updates will be available regularly before and during the conference.
This app is provided by the European Society of Human Genetics.
